             was indicted for <rs id="t17750218-57-off290" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17750218-57-off290" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750218-57-off290" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a man's hat, value one shilling, a man's peruke, value two shillings, a silver watch, value thirty shillings, a steel watch chain, value six-pence, a steel watch key, value two-pence, and a steel watch hook, value two-pence
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17750218-57-victim499" type="victimName">
                     William
                      Daulby
                  <interp inst="t17750218-57-victim499" type="surname" value="Daulby"></interp>
